        {
            "id": 6020085,
            "title": "川普稱中國將開放稀土供應 中國外交部這樣回應",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>美國總統川普 11 日在社群台平上發問表示，中國將預先供應磁鐵和必要稀土，美國也同意讓中國學生就讀美國大學及學院。對此，外媒記者在中國外交部例行記者會上，要求中方證實或提供細節，中國外交部表示，中方一向言必行，行必果。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020085%2Fl%2F22ae65e6fa199fc8550b9683d95e458f.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020085%2Fl%2F22ae65e6fa199fc8550b9683d95e458f.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020085%2Fl%2F22ae65e6fa199fc8550b9683d95e458f.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020085%2Fl%2F22ae65e6fa199fc8550b9683d95e458f.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020085%2Fl%2F22ae65e6fa199fc8550b9683d95e458f.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020085%2Fl%2F22ae65e6fa199fc8550b9683d95e458f.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020085%2Fl%2F22ae65e6fa199fc8550b9683d95e458f.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020085%2Fl%2F22ae65e6fa199fc8550b9683d95e458f.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020085%2Fl%2F22ae65e6fa199fc8550b9683d95e458f.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020085%2Fl%2F22ae65e6fa199fc8550b9683d95e458f.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020085%2Fl%2F22ae65e6fa199fc8550b9683d95e458f.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020085%2Fl%2F22ae65e6fa199fc8550b9683d95e458f.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020085%2Fl%2F22ae65e6fa199fc8550b9683d95e458f.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020085%2Fl%2F22ae65e6fa199fc8550b9683d95e458f.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020085%2Fl%2F22ae65e6fa199fc8550b9683d95e458f.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020085%2Fl%2F22ae65e6fa199fc8550b9683d95e458f.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6020085%2Fl%2F22ae65e6fa199fc8550b9683d95e458f.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">川普稱中國將開放稀土供應 中國外交部這樣回應。(圖:shutterstock)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>川普在貼文中寫道：「我們與中國的協議已完成，尚待我與習主席最終核准。中國將立即完整供應磁鐵產品，以及所有所需的稀土。同樣的，我們將依照協議內容向中國提供相關項目，包括讓中國學生赴美就讀大學（我一直都很支持！）。我們將對中國商品課徵總計 55% 的關稅，而中國則對美國商品課徵 10% 的關稅。雙邊關係非常良好！感謝大家關注此事！」</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>中國外交部發言人林劍，本次會議是在兩國元首的戰略指引下舉行，雙方就落實兩國元首 6 月 5 日通話重要共識和鞏固日內瓦經貿會談成果的措施框架達成一致，就解決雙方原則相互經貿切切。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>林劍表示，中方一向言必行，行必果，既然達成了共識，雙方都應遵守。希望美方同中方一道落實兩國元首通話達成的重要共識，發揮中美經貿磋商機製作用，透過溝通對話，增進共識，減少誤解，加強合作。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
